<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/visitengland> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "VisitEngland (VE) is the national tourist board for England, responsible for marketing England to domestic and established overseas markets and for improving England’s tourism product. VE is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ."@en .
